                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18041024-16-off86 t18041024-16-cd87"></join>, twenty-two yards of printed cotton, value 22 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18041024-16-victim173" type="victimName">
                           Robert 
